data.description: Welcome to this amazing opportunity to own a 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom condo with a perfect blend of modern comfort and outdoor serenity! This condo is complemented by a expansive fenced yard. Located in a desirable neighborhood, the home offers a tranquil retreat in the warmth of this thoughtfully designed living space. The open-concept layout creates perfect flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The owners en-suite offers a well appointed bathroom space, spacious closet and a large window for natural light. The second bedroom is equally inviting, providing a cozy space for guests or a home office.  Immerse yourself in homey comfort, and tranquility—schedule your private viewing today and experience the pinnacle of modern living!
